project_info:
1月11日马来西亚十大DJ之一MIA 空降MOP
[星期六 1月11日] 马来西亚十大 DJ 之一 MIA Q从吉隆坡的夜店到澳门最火爆的场所，DJ Mia Q 已准备好于 1 月 11 日星期六登台表演！
Mia Q 被公认为马来西亚十大 DJ 之一，她以动感十足的风格而闻名——将 house、迷幻舞曲、EDM、硬派风格和 Vina 融合到她的表演中。凭借 Mia 标志性的舞步和富有感染力的能量，她带来的氛围让观众整晚都热血沸腾。
与她一起加入的还有 MOP 的常驻重量级人物，为阵容带来了更多激情。倒计时开始了。让我们一起跳舞吧。
[SAT 11 JAN] Club MOP presents MIA QStraight from Kuala Lumpur’s thriving club circuit to the decks of Macau's hottest venue, DJ Mia Q is ready to take the stage this Saturday, January 11th!Recognised as one of Malaysia’s Top 10 DJs, Mia Q is known for her dynamic range—blending house, psytrance, EDM, hard-styles, and Vina into her sets. With Mia's signature dance moves and infectious energy, she brings a vibe that keeps the crowd moving all night.Joining her are MOP’s resident heavyweights, bringing even more fire to the lineup. The countdown is on. Let’s dance.
门票包含两杯饮品。Entry Fee includes 2 Drinks
